00:57:43.506 --> 00:57:45.255 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And to feel
safe at the same time.

00:57:45.255 --> 00:57:45.530 align:middle line:90%
>>ATTWOOD: That's right.

00:57:45.530 --> 00:57:48.090 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So if some wanted
