set an intention,

00:57:49.840 --> 00:57:51.240 align:middle line:84%
they would need
to have something

00:57:51.240 --> 00:57:53.210 align:middle line:84%
to do with meaning
in their life,

00:57:53.210 --> 00:57:56.470 align:middle line:90%
and what's another aspect of it?

00:57:56.470 --> 00:57:58.980 align:middle line:84%
>>ATTWOOD: Everyday
rituals are really simple,

00:57:58.980 --> 00:58:02.505 align:middle line:84%
