00:58:02.505 --> 00:58:05.220 align:middle line:84%
that you decide I'm
going to take a minute--

00:58:05.220 --> 00:58:05.300 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh, interesting.

00:58:05.300 --> 00:58:07.020 align:middle line:84%
>>ATTWOOD: Or two minutes
when I wake up in the morning,

00:58:07.020 --> 00:58:09.771 align:middle line:84%
