intention for what am I going

00:58:09.771 --> 00:58:10.270 align:middle line:90%
to do--

00:58:10.270 --> 00:58:10.700 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That could
be the ritual.

00:58:10.700 --> 00:58:12.658 align:middle line:84%
>>ATTWOOD: What am I
going to accomplish today?

00:58:12.658 --> 00:58:15.770 align:middle line:84%
Or we all take a
shower-- what if you just

00:58:15.770 --> 00:58:17.460 align:middle line:84%
take-- while you're
taking a shower

00:58:17.460 --> 00:58:18.800 align:middle line:84%
you thought what am
I grateful for today.

00:58:18.800 --> 00:58:20.980 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: This is your time
of prayer or something--yes.

00:58:20.980 --> 00:58:21.980 align:middle line:90%
>>ATTWOOD: That's right.

00:58:21.980 --> 00:58:24.400 align:middle line:84%
So everyday rituals are
things of just saying

00:58:24.400 --> 00:58:25.730 align:middle line:90%
