00:58:36.340 --> 00:58:38.000 align:middle line:90%
have to take up a lot of time.

00:58:38.000 --> 00:58:40.280 align:middle line:84%
Now ceremonial rituals
are more involved.

00:58:40.280 --> 00:58:44.100 align:middle line:84%
And as you know, Lisa, as we
