seven distinct aspects.

00:58:49.760 --> 00:58:53.190 align:middle line:84%
And so you can create a
simple ceremonial ritual.

00:58:53.190 --> 00:58:55.410 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't have to
take a lot of time,

00:58:55.410 --> 00:58:58.220 align:middle line:84%
but it does involve
more aspects than just

00:58:58.220 --> 00:58:59.470 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to set an intention.

00:58:59.470 --> 00:58:59.790 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:58:59.790 --> 00:59:00.665 align:middle line:90%
>>ATTWOOD: You know--

00:59:00.665 --> 00:59:03.540 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's linked
more to tradition.

00:59:03.540 --> 00:59:05.585 align:middle line:84%
>>ATTWOOD: Or things that
